---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<Layout>

  <section class="media-page">
    <h1>Media Resources</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to the Boom Platforms media page! Here you will find our latest press releases, media assets, and news
      coverage. For any additional inquiries or media requests, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:press@boomplatforms.com">press@boomplatforms.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  
    <h2>Press Releases</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="/press/launch-announcement">Boom Platforms Launches to Revolutionize Bitcoin Payments</a><br />
        <small>Published on: January 15, 2024</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/press/boom-wallet-update">Boom Wallet: Now Supporting Stacks Tokens with Enhanced User Experience</a><br
        />
        <small>Published on: February 10, 2024</small>
      </li>
    </ul>
  
    <h2>Media Assets</h2>
    <p>
      Below, you will find downloadable logos, product images, and other media assets that can be used for articles or
      publications:
    </p>
    <div class="media-assets">
      <div class="media-asset">
        <img src="/images/boom-logo.png" alt="Boom Platforms Logo" />
        <a href="/downloads/boom-logo.zip" class="button">Download Logo</a>
      </div>
      <div class="media-asset">
        <img src="/images/boom-wallet-screenshot.png" alt="Boom Wallet Screenshot" />
        <a href="/downloads/boom-wallet-screenshot.zip" class="button">Download Screenshot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <h2>In the News</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://example.com/news/boom-platforms-feature"
          >How Boom Platforms is Making Bitcoin Payments Easy for Everyone</a
        ><br />
        <small>Published on: March 5, 2024 by Example News</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://example.com/news/boom-wallet-innovation"
          >Boom Wallet: The Future of Decentralized Peer-to-Peer Payments</a
        ><br />
        <small>Published on: March 20, 2024 by Crypto Insights</small>
      </li>
    </ul>
  
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you're a member of the media and need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our media team at <a
        href="mailto:press@boomplatforms.com">press@boomplatforms.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .media-page {
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .media-asset {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .media-asset img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .media-asset .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background-color: #ff007f;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
</style>
